reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 4, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great price, fast shipping, nothing broke!
reviews.reviewText: For the price this was a steal!!! It all came in individual bags and then in a big bag nothing was broken. So many options and different looks that you can do with all of these pieces! None of the pieces have broken me out or turned me green!!! My spouse got them for me for my birthday and as soon as I opened them I was shocked they were so shiny and pretty and I fell in love!!! The only thing I am a little worried about is the leaf necklace one of the leaves were a little bent but you can’t tell really bad, so when I wear it I’m going to have to be careful but otherwise for this price you can’t really complain lol!!! Shipping was within 3 days so it was super fast!!! I am very pleased and will definitely order more products through this company!
